author: Ella Torres
title: Coronavirus is 'a lie': Hundreds gather in California to protest stay-at-home orders
description: Hundreds gather in Huntington Beach, California, to protest stay-at-home orders
content:
More than 200 protestors gathered in Huntington Beach, California, in what was the latest demonstration in the United States against stay-at-home orders under the novel coronavirus pandemic.
